Help & FAQ


Do you have a question about your subscription, a recent order, products, shipping or you want to suggest a new magazine? Here you can find some helpful answers to frequently asked questions (FAQ).

General questions

What does LOREM mean?

Where can I subscribe to your newsletter?

Where can in edit my address?

Can I order a free copy of a magazine to sample?

Do you accept orders via Phone or E-mail?

Can I reserve a magazine via Phone or E-mail?

Where on your website can I open a customer account?

Do I need to create an account to make an order?

What are your opening hours?

Do you also have a physical store?


Are you on Twitter, Facebook and other social media platforms?



Why do the prices in the shop sometimes change?

Do I have the right to return an item?

Do you also sell magazines that have been financed by crowdfunding?

General Terms & Conditions (GTC)

Information for Press and Media

Can I change the displayed currency?










Products
I’d like to suggest a new magazine


From which countries do you sell magazines?

Do you sell gift cards?

Why do some of your prices differ from those of other retailers?

Subscriptions
My subscription is expiring. How can I renew it?

Can I also order a subscription starting from a specific issue?

How much notice do I have to give if I want to cancel a subscription?

How can I cancel an active subscription?
You can cancel the subscription at any time in your customer account. However, please note that a
cancellation period applies. If you wish to cancel your subscription, you must let us know at least 30 days before the end of the subscription (the expiration date can be found on your invoice). Otherwise the subscription will be extended automatically.

We are unable to refund the remaining amount if you cancel your subscription at any point before the end of the subscription period.

I have lost my subscription information

The number of issues per year has changed. Why?


Payment
What are your payment methods?



I lost your account data for advance payment/direct bank transfer






I would like to receive an invoice and pay after delivery. Is that possible?

My order could not be completed because there was a problem with the payment









Error 3005 occurred when paying for my order by PayPal






Do you offer volume discounts for orders above a certain amount?

I’m ordering from abroad. Do I have to pay VAT?


Shipping
What are your shipping methods?

Do you ship abroad?

Can I make an order and pick it up?

How much does shipping cost me?


How quickly do you ship?


I’d like to send my order as a gift. Is that possible?


Why are the shipping costs for deliveries abroad disproportionately high?

My order has not arrived. What can I do?




Can I track my order?

Do I have to pay customs or import fees?


ublisher
We’d like to sell our magazine through your shop

We want to send you a sample copy of our magazine but can’t find your address.

What criteria must a magazine meet in order to be included in your range?



We would like to sell our magazine through your shop but we haven’t yet received an answer

Are unsold magazines sent back to the publisher?


Privacy

Where can I find your disclaimer and data privacy?
